      cin rexralbidv rcla4va reeanv caddc co cn0 cz nnz uzid nnnn0 syl2an fveq2
      uzaddcl eleq1d rcla4v cc nncn addcom ancoms eqeltrd inelcm syl6 rexlimivv
      sylbir an4s necon2bd syl5bi expdimp exp3a 3impd rexlimdvv mpd 3exp2 imp32
      ex necon4ad expimpd syl2ani sylbid alrimivv breq2 mo4 sylibr ) CUFKZBALZC
