  ${
    $d J m n u $.  $d X m n u $.  $d Y m n u $.
    tlmconst.1 $e |- X = U. J $.
    $( A constant sequence converges to the constant.  (Contributed by Jeff
       Madsen, 2-Sep-2009.) $)
    tlmconst $p |- ( ( J e. Top /\ Y e. X ) ->
                                    ( NN X. { Y } ) ( ~~>t ` J ) Y ) $=
      ( vm vu vn wcel wa cn cfv wf cv cuz wral wss c1 wceq adantll adantlr ctop
      csn cxp ctlm wbr wrex cnei w3a fconstg snssi syl11anc adantl simpr elnnuz
      fss fvconst2g ssnei snssg biimpar syldan eqeltrd sylan2br ralrimiva fveq2
      1nn adantr raleqdv rcla4ev sylancr 3jca tlmbr mpbird ) AUAHZCBHZIZJCUBZUC
      ZCAUDKUEJBVQLZVNEMZVQKZFMZHZEGMZNKZOZGJUFZFVPAUGKKZOZUHVOVRVNWHVNVRVMVNJV
